data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and charm in this delightful 2 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom bungalow, located just moments away from all the amenities of town living. Home features include hardwood floors throughout, a well appointed kitchen with granite countertops and plenty of storage, perfect dining space, nice sized bedrooms and large windows allowing natural light to shine through! Exterior features lovely front and back porches, mature landscaping, an enclosed backyard for ultimate privacy, an oversized back deck perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing in your own private paradise! Plenty of parking is available with the attached 2 car garage plus driveway space, with additional storage in the detached tool shed. The close proximity town and being located in East Ellijay city limits includes bonuses such as city water/sewer, city garbage pickup, availability of high speed fiber optics internet, cable tv and natural gas.
